des:
Here's a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "LTDoorbell" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account;
(3). Turn on LTDoorbell devices and connect them with "LTDoorbell" app;
(4). Configure these devices in "LTDoorbell" app and change the appropriate name for your devices;
(5). Download the Amazon "Alexa" app in Google Play or iOS App Store, and cocnnect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "LTDoorbell";
(8). Click Enable skill of "LTDoorbell", then input your userename, password on the login page;
(9). Talk to Echo "Alexa, discover devices". Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(10). Now all setup is done.

Here are the voice commands "LTDoorbell" has:

Doorbell:
"Alexa,discover my devices."
"Alexa,show me the doorbell."
